Consent for Participation and Data Use (GDPR)
By submitting this form, you confirm that:
You have been informed about the purpose of this study.
Your participation is voluntary, and you may stop at any time without consequence.
No personal identifying information is collected; your responses will remain anonymous.
Your data will be used solely for research, analysis, and system improvement purposes.
Your data will be stored securely and in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
If you have any questions about your rights or the use of your data, please contact [insert responsible researcher's email or institution contact].
